                "txt": "Apartment´s location is top, just off Passeig de Gràcia. The apartment has a good & simple restauration preserving the original modernist floors & ceilings yet with modern kitchen and bathrooms.\r\nLluis was a great helpful host & proved to be very professional. \r\nHighly recommended.\r\n\r\n"
