                "txt": "Rina was a fantastic host and was super accommodating! Her place is perfectly situated just down the street from town. Her place is a 5 min walk to the grocery store and the rest of all of the nice little shops and restaurants and 2 mins past there is a beautiful beach :)\nWe loved our private room and we felt secure and cozy in our nook :) and the kitchen is awesome! We definitely recommend putting your hat up at Rina's place if you're looking for the sweet spot in Paia ;)\nCheers!"
