                "txt": "My group of four friends and I had a great stay in Regina's Airbnb. The apartment looked just as it did in the listing and was very clean. Regina was easy to communicate with before our stay and she coordinated for her friend Maks to meet us when we arrived. There was plenty of room for the group of five one the apartment. We thoroughly enjoyed the outdoor terrace and spent our mornings out there to eat the breakfast we had prepared in the well equipped kitchen. We did, however, wish there had been some basic kitchen ingredients like salt, spices, or oil there for us to use. The location was a quick walk to Park Güell and it was nice being in a non touristy area. That did however, mean that it was not as easy to reach the city center. "
